s absent from the delegate, or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"if the annotation lacks a title, the annotation will not show a callout even","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"when selected.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Related-examples","level":4,"text":"Related examples"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"TODO: Add annotation views and images","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"TODO: Display custom views as callouts","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"TODO: Default callout usage, learn how to show callouts for","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"text":" objects.","type":"text"}]}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:annotationcanshowcallout:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate"]]},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate":{"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate","isActive":true},{"text":" protocol defines a set of optional methods that you","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"can use to receive map-related update messages. Because many map operations"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"require the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" class to load data asynchronously, the map view calls"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"these methods to notify your application when specific operations complete. The"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"map view also uses these methods to request information about annotations"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"displayed on the map, such as the styles and interaction modes to apply to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"individual annotations.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNMapViewDelegate","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapViewDelegate","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate/mapView:annotationCanShowCallout:":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:annotationCanShowCallout:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns a Boolean value indicating whether the annotation is able to display"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"extra information in a callout bubble."}],"role":"symbol","title":"mapView:annotationCanShowCallout:","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView:annotationCanShowCallout:","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:annotationcanshowcallout:"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNAnnotation","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","title":"MLNMapView","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapView","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit."}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"type":"topic","title":"MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","kind":"symbol"}}}